metadata.description: A GENESiS collection of 1,000 unique 3D art pieces, these NFTs are derived from objects, characters, props, and scenes from Spacestation Animation’s debut episode “PiRATE iSLAND”. This project has been under development for over a year, all art pieces are rigged, animated, and have unique materials, textures, and shaders.
